text: And a huge thanks to all who came to today's forum, streamed online & sent in comments. Your engagement is so important! #netneutrality
Thank you to our fantastic witnesses: @californiapuc Commissioner Sandoval, @thatchriskelly, @davlowe, @Rivkah & @tallgirlmel #netneutrality
Thank you to @MClyburnFCC and @JRosenworcel for joining me in #Sacramento for this great congressional forum on #netneutrality.
#netneutrality congressional forum in Sacramento is wrapping up.  HUGE thank you to @accesssac for providing webcast!
.@Rivkah: As far as I'm concerned the most important thing you can do is eliminate all discussion of paid prioritization. #netneutrality.
.@tallgirlmel: online allows individuals to create content even if the networks turn them down. #netneutrality
.@tallgirlmel: Consumers make the decision on what they want to watch. Paid fast lanes would undermine nature of Internet. #netneutrality
Rep. Matsui asking @tallgirlmel about watching TV online & the need for high speed broadband to stream new shows. #netneutrality
Rep. Matsui asking @thatchriskelly to elaborate on idea of paid prioritization as tax on innovation. Indicates she agrees. #netneutrality
.@californiapuc Commissioner Sandoval: (cont) Burn specialist can study extent of a burn & advise if burn unit is a ways off. #netneutrality
.@californiapuc Commissioner Sandoval: Example- fast internet w. high res cameras is critical to survival of burn victims #netneutrality
Rep. Matsui asking @californiapuc Commissioner Sandoval about importance of open Internet on health care. #netneutrality
Testimony has wrapped up.  Questions are now being posed to witnesses #netneutrality
.@tallgirlmel: Still time to protect the rights of content producers & consumers. We must win the fight for neutrality. #netneutrality
.@tallgirlmel: Will new media be dominated by the gatekeepers that dominated old media. The climax has not yet been written. #netneutrality
.@tallgirlmel: At stake is the ability of screenwriters like myself to tell stories they want to tell. #netneutrality
Great crowd at the Sacramento Congressional forum on #netneutrality! http://t.co/jZzpAgu2l4
.@tallgirlmel, writer & member of @WGAWest is beginning her testimony. #netneutrality
.@davlowe: Online KVIE had 1.2M views through online platforms across US. Online viewing grew 4% to 19% in just 2 yrs #netneutrality
.@davlowe, President & General Manager of @KVIEPBS is beginning his testimony. #netneutrality
.@thatchriskelly: Silicon Valley is ready to assure that #netneutrality is the law of the land
.@thatchriskelly: Unlikely Facebook would have grown from college room w/o the de facto #netneutrality that has existed prior to this point
.@thatchriskelly: Story of internet, is reaching millions of ppl w. ppl being able to reach back to you at a low cost #netneutrality
.@thatchriskelly, founder of Kelly Investments & minority owner of @SacramentoKings is beginning his testimony. #netneutrality
.@rivkah: We support leg. that would prohibit paid prioritization, introduced by you Congresswoman Matsui and Sen. Pat Leahy. #netneutrality
.@rivkah: Paid prioritization would expand the gap between the haves and the have nots #netneutrality
.@Rivkah: An open internet is not a privilege for the affluent, it is a right for all of us. #netneutrality
